{
  "stem": "17299.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she got a shock when she saw me, because I had lost 40 pounds of weight.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told her that the oldest brother had died.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we were put in quarantine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were deloused and put in quarantine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said that I have malnutrition and my blood pressure is too low, is under 100.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I could rejoin my family the next day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got extra food rations.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I stayed in the ghetto for two weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And here, I found out that a lot of relatives had been taken out on the 26th of March, 1942.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that over 90% of the people over 50 years, and over 90% of all the children, had been removed from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were supposed to go to [NON-ENGLISH] in a village on the River Duina.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this was a joke.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They all got killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I was later on in Jungfernhof, come back to-- the same action happened at the same day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in charge of the whole thing was Heinz Jost, commandant of the security police for [NON-ENGLISH], what the German called [NON-ENGLISH], Latvia, Lithuania, Estonia, and White Russia.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto-- hardly any people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw some ghetto police, another piece of paper on the street and a big wire-- barbed-wire fence.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all I saw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They all were in shock when they saw me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Same way.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were even more in shock when I told them what happened to my oldest brother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they asked about other friends and relatives.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told them, I tell you, don't you know what happened to them?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody in the ghetto knew what was going on in Salaspils.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "11 miles.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
